---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="Alpha Gamma Omega | UC Berkeley">
	<main>
		<Header />
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What is AGO?</h2>
					<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Alpha Gamma Omega is the largest college social fraternity in the world, with over 250,000 living members spanning across 17,000 active graduates and nearly 700 chapters and colonies. Founded on Christian principles, AGO has been developing men of character and fostering lifelong brotherhood since its establishment. Our fraternity maintains a strong presence across college campuses nationwide, with our International headquarters located in Charlottesville, Virginia.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
					<div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Beta Chapter</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
							The Alpha Gamma Omega chapter at UC Berkeley is called the Beta Chapter. We are the only Christ-centered fraternity at UC Berkeley and are recognized by the IFC. We are also actively involved in the Greek system, in local churches, and in the Cal community. Many of the active members of the fraternity live at the house, which is 3 blocks from campus. Non-members also live at the house. As Christians, and as a Christ-centered fraternity, we believe that we are called by God to love and serve those around us.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="relative h-[400px]">
						<img 
							src="/ago/pensieve.jpg" 
							alt="Beta Chapter Image" 
							class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-purple-900 uppercase mb-2">Testimonials</h2>
				<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Hear from what our brothers have to say</h3>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">"Alpha Gamma Omega has been a transformative experience, providing lifelong friendships and leadership opportunities."</p>
						<div class="flex items-center">
							<img class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full mr-4" src="/ago/person1.jpeg" alt="Brother 1">
							<div class="text-left">
								<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">John Doe</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Class of 2022, Computer Science</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">"Being part of AGO has enriched my college experience beyond measure, fostering both personal and spiritual growth."</p>
						<div class="flex items-center">
							<img class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full mr-4" src="/ago/person2.jpeg" alt="Brother 2">
							<div class="text-left">
								<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Alex Smith</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Class of 2023, Business Administration</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">"AGO has provided me with a supportive community and opportunities to serve others, aligning with my values."</p>
						<div class="flex items-center">
							<img class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full mr-4" src="/ago/person3.jpeg" alt="Brother 3">
							<div class="text-left">
								<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Michael Lee</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Class of 2021, Mechanical Engineering</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">"The brotherhood and mentorship at AGO have been invaluable, helping me navigate both academic and personal challenges."</p>
						<div class="flex items-center">
							<img class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full mr-4" src="/ago/person4.jpeg" alt="Brother 4">
							<div class="text-left">
								<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Chris Johnson</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Class of 2020, Political Science</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">"AGO has been a cornerstone of my college life, offering a unique blend of faith, friendship, and fun."</p>
						<div class="flex items-center">
							<img class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full mr-4" src="/ago/person5.jpeg" alt="Brother 5">
							<div class="text-left">
								<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">David Kim</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Class of 2024, Biology</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">"Joining AGO was one of the best decisions I've made, providing a network of support and lifelong friendships."</p>
						<div class="flex items-center">
							<img class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full mr-4" src="/ago/person6.jpeg" alt="Brother 6">
							<div class="text-left">
								<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Emily Chen</p>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Class of 2025, Physics</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
					<div class="relative h-[400px]">
						<img 
							src="/ago/pismo.jpg" 
							alt="Rush Group Photo" 
							class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
						/>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Join Alpha Gamma Omega</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
							We are a Christian-centric organization, with each chapter having its own schedule of events and activities. Choosing Alpha Gamma Omega is your first step to brotherhood in a life-changing Christian fraternity that will make an impact in your life.
						</p>
						<div>
							<a 
								href="/rush"
								class="inline-block bg-purple-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-purple-800 transition duration-150 ease-in-out"
							>
								Rush AGO
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-green-600 ">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-100 mb-4">Connect With Us</h2>
				<div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mb-6">
					<a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" class="text-gray-100 hover:text-gray-900">
						<img src="/ago/instagram-color.svg" alt="Instagram" class="h-8 w-8">
					</a>
					<a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" class="text-gray-100 hover:text-gray-900">
						<img src="/ago/x-color.svg" alt="Twitter" class="h-8 w-8">
					</a>
					<a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" class="text-gray-100 hover:text-gray-900">
						<img src="/ago/facebook-color.svg" alt="Facebook" class="h-8 w-8">
					</a>
					<a href="https://youtube.com" target="_blank" class="text-gray-100 hover:text-gray-900">
						<img src="/ago/youtube-color.svg" alt="YouTube" class="h-8 w-8">
					</a>
					<a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="text-gray-100 hover:text-gray-900">
						<img src="/ago/linkedin-color.svg" alt="LinkedIn" class="h-8 w-8">
					</a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-100 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Stay connected with us through our social media channels or reach out for more information.
				</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-purple-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-purple-800 transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
					Contact Page
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>